# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║                     NEZUKO MONOREPO - ENVIRONMENT REFERENCE                   ║
# ║                                                                               ║
# ║  ⚠️  THIS FILE IS FOR DOCUMENTATION ONLY - DO NOT PUT ACTUAL VALUES HERE     ║
# ║                                                                               ║
# ║  Each app has its own environment file:                                       ║
# ║    • apps/web/.env.local   → Next.js Dashboard                                ║
# ║    • apps/api/.env         → FastAPI Backend                                  ║
# ║    • apps/bot/.env         → Telegram Bot                                     ║
